name: Frontend-nanodegree-arcade-game
tagline: Clone of the classic arcade game Frogger.
body:
### Frogger - The Classic Arcade Game
As part of the Udacity Frontend Nanodegree, students are given the building blocks needed to develop a Frogger clone. This project gives experience working with the canvas and working with object-oriented JavaScript.

You can test the game here: [http://silentvibe.com/frogger/](http://silentvibe.com/frogger/)

```
$ cd barnsey007/frontend-nanodegree-arcade-game
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch.
